title: Leading the Double Olympic Champions to the Rugby World Cup!

media:group.media:title: Leading the Double Olympic Champions to the Rugby World Cup!
media:group.media:description:
Ben Gollings took up the role as Fiji 7s head coach, and was immediately tasked with the need for success as the double olympic champions sought their first Rugby World Cup 7s title in 17 years.
In this weeks HSBC Connected he also talks about his long term plan for the island and what he hopes to achieve!

#Rugby #Sevens #Fiji
